{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/linux/ssl-certificates","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"fingerprint--thumbprint\" style=\"position:relative;\">Fingerprint / thumbprint<a href=\"#fingerprint--thumbprint\" aria-label=\"fingerprint  thumbprint permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">openssl x509 -noout -fingerprint -sha1 -inform pem -in api.crt</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"serial-number\" style=\"position:relative;\">Serial number<a href=\"#serial-number\" aria-label=\"serial number permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">openssl x509 -noout -serial -in api.crt</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"expiration-date\" style=\"position:relative;\">Expiration date<a href=\"#expiration-date\" aria-label=\"expiration date permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">openssl x509 -enddate -noout -in api.crt</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"convert-to-java-keystore\" style=\"position:relative;\">Convert to Java keystore<a href=\"#convert-to-java-keystore\" aria-label=\"convert to java keystore permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># Convert the x.509 cert and key to a pkcs12 file</span>\nopenssl pkcs12 <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-export</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-in</span> server.crt <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-inkey</span> server.key <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n  <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-out</span> server.p12 <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-name</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>server-name<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n  <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-CAfile</span> ca.pem <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-caname</span> root\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># Convert the pkcs12 file to a Java keystore</span>\nkeytool <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-importkeystore</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-destkeystore</span> server.jks <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-deststoretype</span> jks <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-deststorepass</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>password<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-destkeypass</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>another password<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-srckeystore</span> server.p12 <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-srcstoretype</span> pkcs12 <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-srcstorepass</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>password from previous step<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-alias</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>short-name-for-the-server<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Verify</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">keytool -list -keystore server.jks</code></pre></div>\n<p>Code exaples:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/code/java/java-tcp-secure-server-socket\">Java TCP secure server socket</a></li>\n</ul>","excerpt":"Fingerprint / thumbprint Serial number Expiration date Convert to Java keystore Verify Code exaples: Java TCP secure server socket","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#fingerprint--thumbprint\">Fingerprint / thumbprint</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#serial-number\">Serial number</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#expiration-date\">Expiration date</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#convert-to-java-keystore\">Convert to Java keystore</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"socialcard":"gatsby-plugin-social-card/16b2809e-edb3-5a4a-9219-08fa5e056dcf.jpg"},"frontmatter":{"date":"January 30, 2022","published":"January 30, 2022","lastModified":"January 30, 2022","title":"SSL Certificates","subtitle":null,"section":null,"draft":null,"developing":null,"buttonText":null,"buttonLink":null,"secondButtonText":null,"secondButtonLink":null,"featuredImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"showLikes":true,"absolutePath":"/home/runner/work/mikolasan.github.io/mikolasan.github.io/src/markdown/linux/ssl-certificates.md","url":"/linux/ssl-certificates","next":{"excerpt":"You can check the major and minor numbers of the CMake version installed on your system using the following command in Bash: The  options…","fileAbsolutePath":"/home/runner/work/mikolasan.github.io/mikolasan.github.io/src/markdown/linux/check-cmake-version-in-bash.md","frontmatter":{"title":"Check CMake version in Bash","date":"2022-05-02T00:00:00.000Z","topic":null,"article":null},"id":"b747c1ae-8a53-5dc2-a23c-e1f5d098fdd8"},"previous":{"excerpt":"Getting time from a remote database can be a simple way to maintain consis